<%- include("partials/header.ejs") %>

<div id="home-title-container">
    <% if(locals.data) { %>
        <h1 id="home-heading" class="page-title">Welcome to NutriFit, <%= data.firstName %> <%= data.lastName %></h1>
    <% } else { %>
        <h1 id="home-heading" class="page-title">Welcome to NutriFit! Please Sign-In</h1>
    <% } %>
    <p id="app-description">
        Nutrifit is all about two things: Nutrition and Fitness. Our goal is to help you reach 
        the goals you have for yourself in everything regarding your health, and that is 
        most effective when combining your nutrition with your fitness. Nutrifit is your space 
        to organize your nutritional and fitness goals and schedules. Not only that, but it is 
        the place where you can receive guidance on the type of nutrition and exercises that 
        will help you achieve your goal, all backed up by real data!
    </p>
    <form id="signin-form" action="/" method="get">
        <button id="signin-button" class="btn1" type="submit">Sign In</button>
    </form>
</div>

<div id="nutrifit-images-container">
    <img id="nutritional-meal-image" class="decorational-images" src="images/nutritional-meal.jpg">
    <img id="gym-chestpress-image" class="decorational-images" src="images/gym-chestpress.jpg">
</div>

<div id="berry-container">
    <h2 id="berry-heading">ASK BERRY</h2>
    <p id="berry-description">
        Berry is our Nutritional and Fitness AI specialist. Taking data from the most credible 
        nutritional and fitness databases and APIs, berry is here to help you understand more 
        about what you need to do to achieve your health goals for a better life. You can ask 
        Berry any questions you might have about Nutrition and Fitness. You can also ask Berry 
        to help you make a meal plan and an exercise routine to help you achieve your health 
        goals. Berry will always guide you behind the reason for each suggestion, and help you 
        create the plan that works for you
    </p>
    <form action="/ask-berry" method="post" id="berry-form">
        <textarea id="prompt" name="prompt" placeholder="Enter your prompt"></textarea>
        <input type="submit" id="submit-prompt" class="btn1" name="submit-prompt" value="Submit Prompt">
    </form>
</div>

